    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle and take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 10-12 min or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
