    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a plate and set aside</p><p>Reserve the pan</p>",
