    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced carrot[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and<strong> halved</strong> <strong>green beans</strong> with your <strong>curry powder </strong>and <strong>garam masala</strong> and cook for 3 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle of oil if your pan is looking a little dry, to help cook out all of the spices!</p>",
