      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, add your<strong> udon noodles</strong> to the pan, gently separating them with a fork</p><p>Return the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min further, stirring until the noodles are coated in the sauce and everything is warmed through – this is your<strong> Japanese-style chicken curry udon</strong></p>",
